OL,6,CG1961FThe Daily Mail reports that Nan
OL,7,FWinton has been dropped from reading
OL,8,Fthe late-night BBC TV news and from the
OL,9,Fnews presenting team, for the second
OL,10,Ftime in recent months. She presented a
OL,11,Fnews bulletin for the final time on
OL,12,F14th March 1961.
